title: 2 Bed in Round Rock ready for you to thrive in
posting_body: With a convenient setting, enticing amenities, and warm friendly atmosphere, this apartment home is hard to beat.
Tucked in a peaceful setting near Brushy Creek and Old Settlers Park.
This pet-friendly two bedroom apartment treats you to an inviting living experience in Round Rock.
Come home to a beautiful open-concept interior highlighted by plank wood flooring, granite countertops, and expansive closets.
Relax and take in the fresh air and views from your private patio.
Whip up delicious meals in your elegant kitchen.
Warm and inviting, this is a space you can truly settle in and feel at home.
Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor
*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.
